description.fr: {%APPEARANCE} Invoque {value:x}\_{Summoning:366,plural:other} sur des cases du bord du plateau. \--- ATTAQUE\_: {#PUSH} la cible de {cell:c}. \--- {%DEATH} Transforme l'{Summoning:650!} le plus éloigné en {Summoning:803!}.
description.en: {%APPEARANCE} Summons {value:x}\_{Summoning:366,plural:other} on cells on the edge of the board. \--- ATTACK: {#PUSH} the target {cell:c}. \--- {%DEATH} Transforms the most distant {Summoning:650!} into {Summoning:803!}.

description.de: {%APPEARANCE} Beschwört {value:x}\_{Summoning:366,plural:other} auf Feldern am Rand des Spielfelds. \--- ANGRIFF: {#PUSH} das Ziel {cell:c} zurück. \--- {%DEATH} Verwandelt den am weitesten entfernten {Summoning:650!} in die {Summoning:803!}.
description.pt: {%APPEARANCE} Invoca {value:x}\_{Summoning:366,plural:other} sobre células na borda do tabuleiro. \--- ATAQUE: {#PUSH} o alvo por {cell:c}. \--- {%DEATH} Transforma o {Summoning:650!} mais afastado em {Summoning:803!}.
